author: perrotta
body:
Rename AntiKT4 as AK4 in all FastJetProducers and related modules of the HLT Run2 menu.
This is needed in preparation of the further integration of the JIRA ticket that updates Jet sequences in the menu.
title: Rename AntiKT4 as AK4 in all FastJetProducers and related modules of the HLT Run2 menu
